; margin-bottom: 1rem; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; text-align: left; color: rgb(14, 14, 15);\">C’est un lieu à la fois de fabrication d’objets et de partage de connaissances. Toute personne, quelque soit son niveau de connaissance et ses moyens, peut venir se servir des machines pour réaliser ses projets personnels, scolaires, ou commerciaux, mais aussi apprendre et partager.</p>		\n				<figure><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/images-3.jpeg\" alt=\"images (3)\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/telechargement-7.jpeg\" alt=\"téléchargement (7)\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/telechargement-4-1.jpeg\" alt=\"téléchargement (4)\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/telechargement-8.jpeg\" alt=\"téléchargement (8)\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/telechargement-4.jpeg\" alt=\"téléchargement (4)\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/telechargement-5.jpeg\" alt=\"téléchargement (5)\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/telechargement-6.jpeg\" alt=\"téléchargement (6)\" /></figure><figure><img src=\"http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/telechargement-1.png\" alt=\"téléchargement (1)\" /></figure>			\n						Précédent\n						Suivant\n			<h2><b>FILIAIRES</b></h2>		\n			<h4>Ressources Humaines<br></h4>		\n										<img width=\"312\" height=\"162\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/telechargement-9.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/telechargement-9.jpeg 312w, http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/telechargement-9-300x156.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 312px) 100vw, 312px\" />											\n			<h4>Développement Web</h4>		\n										<img width=\"318\" height=\"159\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/images-5.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/images-5.jpeg 318w, http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/images-5-300x150.jpeg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 318px) 100vw, 318px\" />											\n			<h4>Design</h4>		\n										<img width=\"318\" height=\"158\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/images.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" srcset=\"http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/images.png 318w, http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/images-300x149.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 318px) 100vw, 318px\" />											\n			<h4>Marketing Digital</h4>		\n										<img width=\"300\" height=\"168\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/telechargement-11.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n			<h4>Comptabilité</h4>		\n										<img width=\"298\" height=\"169\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/images-9.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n			<h4>Modélisation  3D</h4>		\n										<img width=\"299\" height=\"169\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/images-6.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n			<h4>Arduino</h4>		\n										<img width=\"300\" height=\"168\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/images-10.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />											\n										<img width=\"4\" height=\"3\" src=\"http://localhost/wordpress2/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/images-7-e1603876469505.jpeg\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" />', 'ACCUEIL', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '9-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-10-28 13:23:35', '2020-10-28 12:23:35', 